OL,3,CMan says bullying made school 'hell'
OL,4,Cfor him and urges victims to speak out
OL,6,FITV News' Ben McGrail spoke to Ashley
OL,7,Fabout his experiences and hope for the
OL,8,Ffuture
OL,10,FA Taunton man has urged young people
OL,11,Fto speak out if they're being bullied,
OL,12,Fsaying school was hell for him.
OL,14,FAshley Carter, 24, is an anti-bullying
OL,15,Fcampaigner. He was born with Treacher
OL,16,FCollins syndrome, a condition that
OL,17,Faffects his face and says it led to
OL,18,Fhim being picked on in school.
