OL,3,CMan says bullying made school 'hell'
OL,4,Cfor him and urges victims to speak out
OL,6,FHe added: "They say the past is in the
OL,7,Fpast but in my eyes, it's not. It
OL,8,Flives with me up to now.
OL,10,F"Going out, day in, day out. I love my
OL,11,Flife at the moment but it's when I
OL,12,Fbump into people that caused the
OL,13,Fissues for me. It sets my anxiety off
OL,14,F- it just sends me back to that day."
