OL,3,CMan says bullying made school 'hell'
OL,4,Cfor him and urges victims to speak out
OL,6,FAshley says talking about what
OL,7,Fhappened to him has helped and he
OL,8,Fwants to continue speaking out for
OL,9,Fvictims, saying: "To begin with I
OL,10,Fdidn't tell my parents because I
OL,11,Fdidn't know how they would react, but
OL,12,Fit was this one day where I went to go
OL,13,Fand see a friend of mine and I
OL,14,Fliterally got into her street and the
OL,15,Ftwo lads that were bullying me at the
OL,16,Ftime chased me home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
