OL,3,CMan says bullying made school 'hell'
OL,4,Cfor him and urges victims to speak out
OL,6,F"I got home, opened the back door and
OL,7,FI burst into tears in front of my mum
OL,8,Fand I just said 'I can't do it
OL,9,Fanymore.' That's where I started
OL,10,Fopening up to my mum."
OL,12,FShaun Friel, Childline Director said:
OL,13,F"Bullying can take on many different
OL,14,Fforms, and it can happen anywhere
OL,15,Fincluding in school, at home or online.
OL,17,F"With almost 8,000 Childline
OL,18,Fcounselling sessions on the issue over
OL,19,Fthe past year, we inevitably hear from
OL,20,Fyoung people on a daily basis who want
OL,21,Fto talk about bullying.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
