OL,3,CMan says bullying made school 'hell'
OL,4,Cfor him and urges victims to speak out
OL,6,F"It's important that campaigns, such
OL,7,Fas Anti-Bullying Week, exist so we can
OL,8,Fcontinue the conversation of the
OL,9,Feffects this type of behaviour can
OL,10,Fhave on children.
OL,12,F"It can make young people feel
OL,13,Fincredibly lonely, afraid and impact
OL,14,Ftheir mental wellbeing. Childline is
OL,15,Falways here for young people to turn
OL,16,Fto, no matter what the issue. Our
OL,17,Ftrained counsellors will be here 24/7
OL,18,Fover the phone and online."
